name: Magic Lamp - Water Creatures
description:
A spinning lamp that creates a fun, soothing atmosphere in any room. Scenes come alive as the lamp cylinder spins around, lighting up your baby nursery, bedroom, or playroom with bright colors and imaginative themes.

The lamps are hand crafted in Canada using natural materials. Canadian West Coast cedar is used for the frame, and Japanese Washi for the rice paper screen. All designs are hand cut and put onto color paper one by one.
